{"comments":"ColorEditor — Bounded color editing for context menus.\n\n## Design\n\nA stateless color editor that receives color from parent and emits changes.\nUses Schema atoms for bounded values:\n\n- Hue: 0-359 (wraps)\n- Saturation: 0-100 (clamps)\n- Lightness: 0-100 (clamps)\n- Red/Green/Blue: 0-255 (clamps)\n- Opacity: 0-100 (clamps)\n\n## Modes\n\n- Compact: Single color swatch with popover\n- Default: HSL sliders inline\n- Expanded: Full color space tabs (HSL, RGB, HWB, OKLAB, OKLCH)\n\n## Schema Integration\n\nAll values are Schema atoms. No unbounded Number or Int. No escape hatches.\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Render a color editor.\n\nSize determines layout:\n- Compact: Just preview swatch (click to expand)\n- Default: HSL sliders inline\n- Expanded: Full HSL sliders with RGB display\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"msg","kind":null,"skolem":null,"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Array"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","ContextMenu","ColorEditor"],"ColorEditorProp"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"msg","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},"tag":"ParensInType"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Element","Types"],"Element"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"msg","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},"visibility":"TypeVarInvisible"},"tag":"ForAll"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[153,72],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/ContextMenu/ColorEditor.purs","start":[153,1]},"title":"colorEditor"},{"children":[],"comments":"Render HSL-focused color editor.\n","info